<%@ Page Title="About Us" Language="C#" MasterPageFile="~/Site.Master" AutoEventWireup="true" CodeBehind="About.aspx.cs" Inherits="MOLLCommunityClinicWeb1.About" %>

<asp:Content ID="Content1" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">

    <h2>About MOLL Community Clinic</h2>

    <p>
        MOLL Community Clinic is a patient-focused healthcare facility dedicated to providing
        affordable, accessible, and high-quality medical services to individuals and families
        in the community. Our mission is to promote wellness, prevent illness, and deliver
        compassionate care to every patient who walks through our doors.
    </p>

    <p>
        Established with the vision of improving community health outcomes, MOLL Community Clinic
        brings together a team of experienced doctors, nurses, and administrative staff who are
        committed to excellence in healthcare delivery. We specialize in general consultations,
        chronic disease management, maternal care, and preventive health services.
    </p>

    <p>
        At MOLL Community Clinic, we believe that healthcare should be both personal and professional.
        We strive to create a welcoming environment where patients feel heard, respected, and cared for.
        Your health is our priority.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4>Our Core Values</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Compassionate Patient Care</li>
        <li>Integrity and Transparency</li>
        <li>Excellence in Medical Service</li>
        <li>Community Wellness and Education</li>
    </ul>

</asp:Content>